items.name: MovieStillXL - by Via
items.description:
Movie Still XL V2!!

Please consider leaving a rating if you like it!

Movie Still XL is made for SDXL and its intended purpose was to add variety and coherence on the already great film and movie still images that are already integrated into SDXL. I am trying to reduce the need to prompt long film style prompts to achieve true movie like generations and with this lora it seems to work quite well.

This model was trained on 1344x768 images. The effects of other aspect ratios may be poor.

V2 NOTE: This model may produce green and pink tinting, if you are having trouble try this negative

'(blurry:1.4), (noisy:1.5) amputated, mutated, ugly, bad image, noisy, crispy, artifacts, tinted green, tinted pink'

What are the potential benefits from this lora?

  • Better "movie like" highlights

  • Better coherence "straighter straights, more consistency" (text and buildings are a little better)

  • Adds a filmic and movie like "Tone" to the final image

What are the potential downsides to this LoRa?

  • This lora can introduce a blur when it is turned up passed 1.0 strength

  • Sense this is still in early stage of development my dataset is still rather small so keep that in mind. This is basically an alpha version. Feel free to comment what else it needs!

  • Some images come out very grainy while some don't, results may vary

What are some of the trigger words?

  • Movie Still - the main trigger word to use the LoRa

  • over the shoulder shot - commonly used with a power of 1.5 to trigger that specific shot

  • 2 people and conversation - increased chance for there to be 2 people in a conversation

  • side view - increased chance to make the person side view probably mixed with 2 people

  • In Focus - Adds detail to background and makes it more in focus. maybe..

  • Action shot - adds action! this is already in sdxl but its also added to the lora itself.

That being said, again this is still in early development, this is my first published LoRa and I hope everyone who downloads likes it! I will be posting updated versions if I see an improvement as the dataset grows.

Recommended Usage:

Sytans SDXL v1.0 workflow in ComfyUI:

https://github.com/SytanSD/Sytan-SDXL-ComfyUI

Best output:

The best output that ive got was from not using the refiner. I run the base model twice with the lora on >>> upscale 4x_NMKD superscale >>> downscale to a reasonable size >>> Do another 10 steps on the base with the upscaled image.



Strength: 0.85 to 1 ... higher than 1.0 can cause blurring or artifacts. use as you wish. may lead to some creepy stuff..

Thank you to Caith and masslevel for helping me with this LoRa!

items.name: Pretty Girls Next Door
items.description:
Pretty girls next door. Trained on 4500 images (dataset attached to download) from well-known softcore nude art websites, mix of manual captions and LLAVA autocaptions with manual tag guidance. Focus is on natural language prompting and flexibility and precision with clothing and nudity.

All of the samples are made with diffusers. Generation only, no inpainting or img2img. Seeds are CPU ("random number generator source" option in automatic1111 or "generator source" option in vladmandic).

Usage guide

Recommended settings

Download the .yaml or you'll get black images. If you want to reproduce the samples use InvokeAI or vladmandic with diffusers backend.

  • DPM++ 2M SDE Karras, CFG 6, 24 steps or 30 steps

  • DPM++ SDE Karras, CFG 6, 24 steps or 30 steps

  • DDIM or Euler a, CFG 6-11, 48-96 steps

Recommended negative: 3d render, ugly, misshapen, corpse, brushstrokes

How to Prompt

The model was trained on multiple sentences separated by full stops, and if you prompt like that you will get more out of it. Eg "a photograph of a woman on the beach, wearing a bikini. beautiful soft rim light, intricate details, 8k."

Prompting walkthrough

Start simple. Don't use tag lists, just write something short like "photo of a naked woman at the beach":

To get closer, add more words for skin or body parts, but this can make generation weird:

To fix weirdness add a pose to the prompt:

Bring the face back into frame by prompting it:

To move further back, add background details:

You an also change the influence of background details by moving them to a different place in the prompt. If they're closer to the start they will have more influence.

More tips

  • Increase quality with words like "ultra realistic, skin details, skin pores, 8k, intricate details".

  • "Detailed face" or just "face" improves faces, "eyes" improves eyes, "lips" improves mouth shape.

    • "Painted eyes" and "cartoon face" in negative help if the eyes look like they're painted on

  • Long negatives are often worse. Start short and add words as bad things appear. Clean up words that are doing nothing as you go.

  • Prompt a pose to improve results (try to match what the random seed is drawing on its own)

    Prompt leg pose to improve results (try to match what the random seed is drawing on its own)

  • Sometimes "professional photograph" "stunning photograph" "detailed photograph" help, sometimes they make the image worse.

  • Sometimes the model gets too close up. Use negative prompt "close up" to fix

  • Some things are overtrained in the base model, especially "bedroom", so move it further down the prompt or downweight it with [[bedroom]]

  • Adding words like "face" or "breasts" or "hips" or "knees" brings camera closer to those things (or further out of they're not in frame already)

  • The first word has a large influence on results. Try "HQ photo", "ultra realistic photo", "professional photo", "digital photo", "detailed photo", "stunning photo", and just "photo"

  • Adding camera, lens, or film words eg "Canon EOS Rebel, f/11 35mm" or "ektachrome ER film" sometimes helps, but sometimes make the output less nude

  • If some things are dominating, change the order of words.

  • Sheer/wet can benefit from "sheer clothing", "see-through", "wet clothing", "visible nipples"

  • Try "open" clothing, eg "open shirt", "open robe". Also try "unbuttoned" and "unzipped" - "wearing an unzipped one piece swimsuit" is fun.

  • Increase cleavage with "cleavage" or a longer phrase like "a tank top that shows her cleavage"

  • To fix cut-off legs or arms put "stump" or "amputee" in negative, or "weird anatomy" or "strange anatomy" or "bad anatomy" 

  • "Good anatomy", "beautiful composition" sometimes helps

Trained words

Face

pretty face, cute face, beautiful face, ugly face (for negative)

Pose

reliable: standing, kneeling, squatting
ok: on all fours, sitting
unreliable: prone (lying on stomach), supine (lying on back), recumbent (lying on side)

Body: 

large breasts, medium breasts, small breasts, cleavage, cute butt, round butt, broad hips

View:

front view, 3/4 view, side view, rear 3/4 view, rear view, low angle, high angle, overhead shot, medium shot

Scene: (also good for negative)

At the pool, at the beach, at a river, in the shower, in the bath, in a photo studio

Legs pose (can be combined with pose, doesn't always work): 

legs together, legs apart, legs spread, legs crossed

Clothing (some work better than others):

Whole body: dress, overcoat, robe, bathrobe, pajamas
Top: tank top, t-shirt, shirt, jumper, sports bra, jacket, hoodie, halter top, polo shirt
Bottom: leggings, jeans, skirt, shorts, sarong, socks, sneakers
Swimwear: bikini, bikini top, bikini bottoms, one piece swimsuit, wetsuit
Underwear: bodysuit, bra, panties, nightgown, slip
Face: glasses, sunglasses, hat

Expressions (unreliable):

duchenne smile, friendly smile, flirty smile, fake smile, polite smile, laughing, confident, distracted, aroused, annoyed, embarrassed, bored, scared, dominating

Clothing state:

Wet, mesh, sheer (combine for better effect eg "wet mesh sheer see-through t-shirt"), fishnet, thin, open, unbuttoned, unzipped, undressing, unbuttoning, unzipping

Pussy (can be combined like "hairy puffy pussy"):

Hairy pussy, shaved pussy, bald pussy, tulip pussy, puffy pussy, curtains pussy, horseshoe pussy

Extras:

Wet skin, with her arms raised, with her hand on her hip, nipple pokies (unreliable), strap slipping off her shoulder, lifting her shirt, hiding her pussy between her legs

Updates

I have updates to the data source planned when I can find some time to work onthem:

  • Add sports bra rear view

  • Fix nipple pokies?

  • Fix undressing?

  • Dress, long with legs not visible (leg poses under dress)

  • Sheer sports bra?

  • Check for "legs crossed" and "legs together" overlap, and "legs together" "legs apart" overlap

  • Add bikini + small breasts

  • Why is "slip" so weirdly close-up?

本人最喜欢的模型之一cuteYuki对萝莉体型表现优秀，但是并不能很好的描绘少女，于是我手动采用多次分层融合变换身型，产出cuteTMix和cuteTMix2,本模型旨在保留cuteYuki可爱的面部，使其具有更成熟的体型。

使用少量提示词即可创造出一幅精美图片，过分提高场景描绘比例会使人物细节流失。

注：该模型会有肢体损失，乃正常情况，先抽抽卡吧，有时间我会修的，有时间的话

The following is translated by GPT:

Parameter suggestions: Steps: 30, Sampler: DPM adaptive, CFG scale: 7-10, Denoising strength: 0.2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B.

This model compared to cuteTMix has a body shape closer to a loli, and accordingly, it retains more of cuteYuki's facial features. In fact, I find this model cuter, so I use it more often.

One of my favorite models, cuteYuki, performs excellently in depicting a loli body type, but it doesn't do well in portraying a young girl. Therefore, I manually used multiple layered fusion transformations to create cuteTMix and cuteTMix2. The purpose of this model is to preserve cuteYuki's adorable facial features while giving it a more mature body shape.

With just a few prompts, you can create a beautiful image; however, excessively increasing the scene depiction ratio may result in the loss of character details.

Note: This model may have limb losses, which is normal. Let's try it out first, and I will fix it when I have time. If I have time, that is.

items.name: 【再世】next life-程思寒
items.description:
这是群星再世第五十九期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

说起程思寒这个名字，绝大部分人可能都不知道，但一说起他演过的角色，可能所有人都会觉得眼熟。广为人知的角色包括《武林外史》金不换、《风云争霸》食为天、《风云雄霸天下》第三猪皇、《水浒传》笑面虎朱富、《小鱼儿与花无缺》中的恶人李大嘴、《西游·降魔篇》中饰演野僧人，《女人花》刘剑雄，《名扬花鼓》祝茂、《十三格格》奕达、《最后的格格》庞万山等，每一个都是80后，90初一代人的童年回忆。

从事演艺事业多年，程思寒塑造的角色差距都很大，大多数都是反面角色，通过他出色的演义，使形象各异而又生动鲜活的人物成为剧中不可或缺的“调味”，给观众留下了深刻的印象。

2019年，程思寒因突发心肌梗塞抢救无效离世，享年58岁。

items.name: Furation
items.description:
MODEL GUIDE

WHAT MODEL SHOULD I CHOOSE?

I suggest The Pear model becuase it overall is the best model, with how you can either use the intricate prompts (which i used in the images for the model's card), or basic prompts.

Boring RANDOM notes:

A continuation of my other model- CrossLawlasMix, but with more models mixed in selectively to make sure it would be the best quality AND I would be able to set the permissions to what I thought would be good.

VANILLA IS THE FIRST STYLE/VERSION meaning the next models MAY or MAY NOT improve on quality.

All of the images were created using Adetailer

Here is the HuggingFace Repo -> Here! <-

DOCUMENTATION ON MODEL (how to use the Model)

SECTION #1 Prompting:

Prompting for this model is quite veritile BUT this positive prompt usually helps making your results better

(best quality, highest quality, digital art, intricate, highres, 8k, anthropomorphic, furry, uploaded_on_e621:1.4), <WHAT YOU WANT HERE>

And For the Negative prompt I recomend this:

(worst quality, low quality, normal quality:1.6), watermark, artist logo, signature, patreon, text, simple background, sepia, simple eyes, empty eyes, no pupils, multi limb, multi arm, multi leg, transformation, blurred background, blurred foreground, sketch, (bad quality, deformed, bad eyes, lowres), boring_e621_fluffyrock_v4:1.5, boring_e621_v4:1.5, FastNegativeV2:1.5, NGH:1.5, negative_hand-neg:1.5,

Also Ps, you are going to need the negative embeddings, unless you want bad results.

SECTION #2 Generation settings:

Higher Steps = better image

Lower CFG = more creative BUT more inaccurate

I suggest you use:

Steps: 35-40, Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 7

but if you want you can use:

Steps: 20-28 , Sampler: Eular a, CFG scale: 7

SECTION #3 Upscaling:

Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B (Or really any anime style upscaler), Denoising strength: 0.3,

More boring stuff:

You can use this on a generation service AS LONG AS IT IS DOES NOT COST REAL MONEY!

items.name: RunDiffusion XL
items.description:
Introducing RunDiffusion XL Beta!

RunDiffusion.com has done it again! One of the worlds first SDXL Models!

Join our 15k Member Discord where we help you with your projects, talk about best practices, post exciting updates and news, and share the amazing art we generate.

Why? Isn't SDXL already amazing?

Yes! We feel this is a step up! SDXL has an issue with people still looking plastic, eyes, hands, and extra limbs. We couldn't solve all the problem (hence the beta), but we're close! We tested hundreds of SDXL prompts straight from Civitai.com (using ComfyUI) to make sure the pipelines were identical and found that this model did produce better images! See for yourself here.

The model tends to favor closeups or "headshots" more than full body unless you explicitly prompt for that. Not sure if that is a desired feature. Open for feedback on that.

Strengths

  • More photorealistic for animals, cars, and people.

  • Different Model, different generations. Try it with your favorite prompt!

  • Better portraits. SDXL likes to put the subject way far out. This brings things closer.

  • Eyes and hands are a bit better (from our testing)

  • Better prompt control. Make sure to use commas and break apart subjects and styles!

Weaknesses

  • Still a few concepts that are "plastic" (Food, but please test your prompts and let us know!)

  • Can sometimes be too "person bias"

  • Creativity is a little bit hindered. This could be considered a "Photorealistic" model. But again, TEST!

  • Bias towards "sports cars" lol

Notice the RDXL follows the prompt a bit better. When asking for "upper body" it tends to follow that.

How to Use

  • Prompt as usual. Use commas to separate subjects and styles. If you aren't getting what you want, use the token again. e.g. iron man made of lava, suit of armor infused with molten lava, ...etc if you don't get Iron Man in your generation, then put that token somewhere else, `iron man made of lava, suit of armor infused with molten lava, marvel iron man super hero ...etc`

  • Use the standard refiner or the 1.0-0.9 refiner. https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-refiner-1.0/blob/main/sd_xl_refiner_1.0_0.9vae.safetensors

  • Use ComfyUI

Our Process

We used a small dataset of 700 images and trained for 14k steps at 20 epochs. Manually captioning everything to be as descriptive as possible. It turns out that SDXL is pretty receptive to training! The changes we were able to make prove to be extremely exciting. The future is bright for SDXL!

Future Plans

We want to make generations easy, so we're bringing ComfyUI to the platform so you can simply drop in images with metadata to generate with one click. This is the future of workflow sharing and we're very grateful to /u/comfyanonymous for his help with getting this working on our platform. Also a special thanks to /u/Searge for his amazing work on SeargeSDXL. We love that workflow! (Could we work on getting the generation data to work on Civitai.com?)

We will continue to work on this model from the feedback we receive. Get ready for a full release in the coming weeks.

Hogan's Heroes is an American television sitcom set in a prisoner-of-war (POW) camp in Nazi Germany during World War II. It ran for 168 episodes (six seasons) from September 17, 1965, to April 4, 1971, on the CBS network, the longest broadcast run for an American television series inspired by that war.

Bob Crane starred as Colonel Robert E. Hogan, coordinating an international crew of Allied prisoners covertly running a special operations group from the camp. Werner Klemperer played Colonel Wilhelm Klink, the gullible commandant of the camp, and John Banner played the blundering but lovable sergeant-of-the-guard, Hans Schultz.

Three of Heroes' funny fascists—Werner Klemperer (Colonel Klink), John Banner (Sergeant Schultz), and Leon Askin (General Burkhalter)—were Jews who survived the Holocaust, while Robert Clary (Corporal LeBeau) had been interned at Buchenwald and lost his parents at Auschwitz.

On June 29, 1978, Victoria Ann Berry, one of Crane’s co-actors, called 911 after discovering his body.Police found the room covered in blood from wall to ceiling and were unable to identify Crane due to the extent of his injuries. Bob Crane was found bludgeoned to death at 49 years old. His killer remains elusive.

items.name: Spooky (Ahegaokami)
items.description:
Finally! My masterpiece is done!! After years (*actually like, half a week) of work, my first Lora is finished!

...Ahem, sorry for that. So, I've finally made my first Lora, and I think it came out pretty good!

So, as you could probably guess, this Lora finally brings the original character of the artist "Ahegaokami", Spooky, to the arena! Tbh, I really love this character and was very surprised to see it wasn't made yet, so I decided to make it myself! And believe me, it was harder than I thought, but we'll get to that later.

So, to the basics:

How do I activate the Lora?

Simple: just use the activation line as every other Lora! (It should be <lora:Spooky_Ahegaokami-10:1> at the time of writing). By the way, this Lora works best used with the MeinaHentai checkpoint, so try it out for the best results! I found that it captured the style of it really well. And another btw, I used the lora at 1 weight, and I think that it works best, but you're welcome to try out other weights to see which ones work best for you!

Special tags (it wouldn't be a Lora without some!):

Spooky: The base of the Lora. Absolutely must use to activate it.

Heart-shaped pupils, heart: prominent tags used when training. Aren't a must have, but can help the Lora a bit, and also just work well.

Extras!: There are some extra tags that work great and were trained thoroughly. These are:

Half-closed eyes (for the effects you can see in the pictures), open eyes (for the eyes to be wide open), loving smile (for a wide, light smile), euphoric (for a melting smile that's "euphoric"? That's the best word I have to describe it), horn grab (I don't have to explain this one, do I? Also, should always be used with "pov" and "pov hands"), breasts out (for the breasts out of a hoodie, or general with other clothes. Should use with "nipples" to work correctly. Also, no need to use if using "completely nude").

*Note: when trying to generate a picture with a penis, use "1boy, penis", and when generating sex of any kind, use "hetero" too for better results. Additionally, when making a pov with a penis (for example, a blowjob), use "male pubic hair" for good results. I hope it's not overwhelming so far, sorry 😔

More, more!: Even more tags include:

Fangs (to be used with "teeth"), skin fang, completely nude, black thighhighs, hoodie, black hoodie, blue hoodie, hood, hood off, cat lingerie, cat ear panties, cat ear thighhighs, heart choker, close up, pov, pov hands, off shoulder, bare shoulders, furrowed brow, nervous smile, wavy mouth, looking aside, embarrassed, tearing up, submissive, etc.

**Note no.2: Ok, I'm sorry, I know this is a bit much, but bear with me, I'll keep it short. Due to most of the trained images having text bubbles, you should add "speech bubble" and "english text" to your negative prompt.

Holy hell, thanks for reading so far! This is my first experience with making a Lora, so any advice or what to change, fix, and how to improve this Lora would be taken in full-heartedly. So don't be shy, I'm all ears!
